{"article_id":"f5ZkO1FqdKZTIIMx","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Minnesota Rep. Michele Bachmann 's announcement Wednesday","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"that she wo n't seek a fifth term","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"unleashed a torrent of tweets and blog posts on the left","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"lampooning the short-lived 2012 presidential candidate .","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"Yet the response","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"- her retirement effectively dominated the news cycle -","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"provided a glimpse of Bachmann 's impact on Washington .","depth":3},{"id":7,"text":"While she amassed a fat portfolio of missteps and fabrications since her 2006 election ,","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"the political provocateur and conservative Christian also secured a place in political history","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"by riding the Tea Party wave early ,","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"and parlaying an unrepentant , cable-ready persona and House seat to national conspicuousness .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"Even detractors allow","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"that her audacity helped open the door for conservative female candidates and for new Republican Tea Party favorites ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"including Texas Sen. Ted Cruz and , to some extent , Florida Sen. Marco Rubio .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"And she established herself as a fundraising juggernaut ,","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"raising nearly $ 15 million for her win-by-a-whisker race in 2012 against Democrat Jim Graves .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"He spent about $ 2.3 million in a race","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"that was nationalized by her polarizing politics .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"`` She was definitely a presence , ''","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"says conservative blogger Dan Riehl ,","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"who added","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"that he chose to `` ignore most of the calamity , the gaffes ''","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"that have punctuated her political career .","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"`` She was a voice against the Republican establishment , a thorn in its side , ''","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"he says .","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"`` In certain ways , she was an iconic figure - effective","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"just because she was there ...","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"She was kicking on the door early","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"and was isolated .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"You have some people","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"benefiting from the heat","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"she took . ''","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"It was n't her effectiveness as a legislator that propelled Bachmann 's national profile :","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"She rated as a House backbencher during her time on Capitol Hill .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"But she founded the House Tea Party Caucus ,","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"became a face of the emerging movement ,","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"and made `` repeal Obamacare '' her clarion call ,","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"thus guaranteeing a role on the national stage .","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"`` Congresswoman Bachmann was able to skillfully use the media , particularly cable media ,","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"to articulate a very conservative message ,","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"and articulate opposition to the Obama administration in ways","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"that went well beyond that of mainstream Republicans , ''","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"says Kathryn Pearson , an American politics expert and associate professor at the University of Minnesota .","depth":5},{"id":43,"text":"`` She did not do a lot legislatively ;","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"it was n't her focus , ''","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"Pearson says ,","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"`` but she gave voice to Tea Party members","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"and made life difficult for her party 's leadership . ''","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"Bachmann ,","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"who in 2011 gave the first televised Tea Party response to a presidential State of the Union address ,","depth":5},{"id":50,"text":"proved impervious to persistent scolding by fact-checking organizations for misstatements and her often tenuous grasp of facts .","depth":4},{"id":51,"text":"She won national notoriety with her sharp rhetoric on cable television news shows ,","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"where she once observed","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"that Obama may have `` anti-American views . ''","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"Tax burdens ?","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"In her view ,","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"they were comparable to the Holocaust .","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"She also asserted","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"that former House Speaker Nancy Pelosi made taxpayers foot the bill for a $ 100,000 in-flight bar tab","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"- another claim","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"that was proven false .","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"That penchant for hyperbole , if not out-right falsity , made her ubiquitous in the cable TV arena","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"but tarnished her reputation as a serious political player","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"and made a wide swath of her home state Republicans cringe .","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"`` To the degree","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"that she was a laughingstock","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"- that 's not good","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"when you 're a Republican in Minnesota , ''","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"says Sarah Janecek , a GOP activist and founder of Politics in Minnesota , a state public affairs news service .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"Bachmann was n't always good for national Republicans either ,","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"as the party attempted to broaden its appeal .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"She proved to be a reliable villain for Democrats ,","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"who often used her over-the-top comments","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"to fuel their own direct-mail fundraising efforts .","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"`` She was a polarizing figure","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"and has drawn a lot of fire ,","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"and made some missteps , ''","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"says Riehl , the conservative blogger .","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"`` The Tea Party movement , however , in some ways , has moved ahead of her now ,","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"grown beyond her ,","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"and is not as handcuffed to the social right . ''","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"Even so , Bachmann 's improbable , audacious run for the presidential nomination in 2012 still resonates with Riehl and other Republicans .","depth":6},{"id":82,"text":"She was n't the first conservative bomb-thrower from the House","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"to run for president ,","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"but she proved a more viable candidate than any other","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"before her campaign fizzled prior to the Iowa caucuses .","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"`` Say what you want ,","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"but she was a woman","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"making her way into an all-boys ' club ,","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"and","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"because she was on the right ,","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"she did n't have women 's groups","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"rallying around her , ''","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"Riehl says .","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"`` She was there on her own . ''","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"Says Janecek :","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"`` Love her or hate her ,","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"Michele Bachmann did herself proud .","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"She was the only woman at the podium during those","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"[ presidential ]","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"debates ,","depth":13},{"id":101,"text":"she looked like a million bucks ,","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"and she had something","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"to say . '' `` When Michele decided she wanted something , ''","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"says Janecek ,","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"who first interviewed Bachmann","depth":14},{"id":106,"text":"when she ran for the state Senate ,","depth":14},{"id":107,"text":"`` It was balls to the wall . ''","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"Now ,","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"with her presidential campaign activity under investigation","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"and facing another tough challenge by Graves ,","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"Bachmann decided","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"another term is not something","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"she wants .","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"To her fans , she remains a singular and steadfast figure .","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"`` Michele Bachmann was someone","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"who ran on principles","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"and lives those principles , ''","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"says Jake Duesenberg ,","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"who heads the East Metro Tea Party organization","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"that reaches into her district .","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"Bachmann gave her detractors a lot of material ,","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"he says ,","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"but earlier this month 400 people turned out","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"to see her at a local Tea Party gathering .","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"`` She packed the house , ''","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"Duesenberg says .","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"`` You can say this or that about how she messages ,","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"but she stood up for free markets , fiscal responsibility and respect for the Constitution . ''","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":257,"left":135,"right":256,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":135,"left":132,"right":134,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":132,"left":130,"right":131,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":130,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearit